#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "aRts"
msgstr "aRts"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sound framework in &kde; 2 and 3. Its single-tasking nature caused "
"problems when two sources of sound were encountered. In the &plasma; desktop "
"it is replaced by Phonon.&newpara; More info:&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ARts\"&linkmid; Wikipedia: ARts&linkend;"
msgstr ""
"Zvočni okvir v &kde; 2 in 3. Njegova enonamenska narava je povzročala "
"težave, ko sta se pojavila dva vira zvoka. V namizju &plasma; ga nadomesti "
"Phonon.&newpara; Več informacij:&newpara; &linkstart; \"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/ARts\"&linkmid; Wikipedia: ARts&linkend;"

#. Tag: glossdef
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
