#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "D-Bus"
msgstr "D-Bus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"D-Bus or Desktop Bus is an inter-service messaging system. Developed by "
"&RedHat;, it was heavily influenced by &kde; 3 DCOP, which it supersedes. "
"Most POSIX operating systems support D-Bus, and a port for Windows exists. "
"It is used by Qt 4 and GNOME.&newpara; More info:&newpara; &linkstart;"
"\"https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/dbus/\"&linkmid;FreeDesktop.org: "
"What is D-Bus?&linkend;&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"D-Bus\"&linkmid;Wikipedia: D-Bus&linkend;"
msgstr ""
"D-Bus ali Namizno vodilo je sistem za sporočanje med storitvami. Razvil ga "
"je &RedHat;, nanj pa je močno vplival &kde; 3 DCOP, ki ga je nadomestil. "
"Večina operacijskih sistemov POSIX podpira D-Bus, za Windows pa je na voljo "
"tudi vmesnik. Uporabljata ga Qt 4 in GNOME.&newpara; Več informacij:"
"&newpara; &linkstart; \"https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/dbus/"
"\"&linkmid;FreeDesktop.org: Kaj je D-Bus?&linkend;&newpara; &linkstart; "
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/D-Bus\"&linkmid;Wikipedia: D-Bus&linkend;"

